column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/25ef6ace70897517fc1d65b1e438a59909bcf1de for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
